				<div></div><div>OK I was playing with the Yoda Calculator again since I finally finally picked up my BBoB last night.  2 dropped just before I apped, go two and a half months or so without one, then 2 more drop.  Go go Random Number Generator!  Anyone else notice Tacvi mobs tend to double up their loot rewards?</div><div> </div><div><font size="2" color="#000000">1</font><font size="2" color="#000000">Brutish Blade of Balance </font><font size="2" color="#000000">13246</font></div><div><font size="2" color="#000000">2</font><font size="2" color="#000000">Fleshbiter </font><font size="2" color="#000000">13217</font></div><div><font size="2" color="#000000">3</font><font size="2" color="#000000">Darkblade of the Warlord </font><font size="2" color="#000000">12960</font></div><div><font size="2" color="#000000">4</font><font size="2" color="#000000">Swiftcleave, the Flesh Carver </font><font size="2" color="#000000">12829</font></div><div><font size="2" color="#000000">5</font><font size="2" color="#000000">Steam-Powered Cogblaster </font><font size="2" color="#000000">12543</font></div><div><font size="2" color="#000000">6</font><font size="2"><font color="#000000">Notched Blade of Bloodletting </font></font><font size="2" color="#000000">12028</font></div><div><font size="2" color="#000000">7</font><font size="2" color="#000000">Aged Smoldering Cudgel </font><font size="2" color="#000000">11854</font></div><div><font size="2" color="#000000">8</font><font size="2" color="#000000">Kreljnok's Sword of Eternal Power </font><font size="2" color="#000000">11672</font></div><div><font size="2" color="#000000">9</font><font size="2" color="#000000">Envenomed Ritualistic Dagger </font><font size="2" color="#000000">11558</font></div><div><font size="2" color="#000000">10</font><font size="2" color="#000000">Thunderclap </font><font size="2" color="#000000">11251</font></div><div><font size="2" color="#000000">11</font><font size="2" color="#000000">Twinfang, the Immortal's Bane </font><font size="2" color="#000000">10939</font></div><div><font size="2" color="#000000">12</font><font size="2" color="#000000">Bone-Rending Battle Sword </font><font size="2" color="#000000">10929</font></div><div><font size="2" color="#000000">13</font><font size="2" color="#000000">Haru's Sand-Etched Sword </font><font size="2" color="#000000">10899</font></div><div><font size="2" color="#000000">14</font><font size="2" color="#000000">Bloodfrenzy </font><font size="2" color="#000000">10872</font></div><div><font size="2" color="#000000">15</font><font size="2" color="#000000">Greater Spiked Staff </font><font size="2" color="#000000">10775</font></div><div><font size="2" color="#000000">16</font><font size="2" color="#000000">Dragonkiller * </font><font size="2" color="#000000">10721</font></div><div><font size="2" color="#000000">17</font><font size="2" color="#000000">Crystal Dagger </font><font size="2" color="#000000">10634</font></div><div><font size="2" color="#000000">18</font><font size="2" color="#000000">Sister's Opulent Backstabber </font><font size="2" color="#000000">10611</font></div><div><font size="2" color="#000000">19</font><font size="2" color="#000000">Spiked Steel Baton </font><font size="2" color="#000000">10605</font></div><div><font size="2" color="#000000">20</font><font size="2" color="#000000">Runic Bloodstained Maul </font><font size="2" color="#000000">10597</font></div><div><font size="2" color="#000000">21</font><font size="2" color="#000000">Blasphemous Blade of the Exiled </font><font size="2" color="#000000">10524</font></div><div><font size="2" color="#000000">22</font><font size="2" color="#000000">Edge of Eternity </font><font size="2" color="#000000">10504</font></div><div><font size="2" color="#000000">23</font><font size="2" color="#000000">Hammer of Rancorous Thoughts </font><font size="2" color="#000000">10500</font></div><div><font size="2" color="#000000">24</font><font size="2" color="#000000">Hammer of th