its using my set up, Fero V, 20 CE, and EB/CSIV augs in Type 4/8 slots)</div><div> </div><div>There's about a 2K hate drop off from #1 to number 10.  I don't recognize some but I'd imagine at least half the top 10 is 3 expansions old or older.  At least 60% of the top 5 is from Omens (2004) or older.  One is from PoP.  2003?</div><div> </div><div>The Top 10 goes from ~13K to ~11K.  The next 23 weapons are all some shade of ~10K hate per minute.  #14 on the list is from freakin Luclin.</div><div> </div><div>Please tell me some Dev will see this, and decide that maybe we are due for some itemization improvements.</div>
				
