				<td rowspan=2 class="msg_text_cell" style="text-align: justify;" width="100%" valign=top>
				<div></div><p>Do the math...it's real easy.</p><p>Taking the 2.2 number with max haste of 100%... you would calculate as follows:</p><p>1.6seconds per round (1.55 rounded to the nearest 10th)</p><p>58 Hate per swing (DMG + Dmg Bonus, or 43+15)</p><p>127.6 hate per round</p><p>37.5 rounds per Minute</p><p>4785 hate per minute in melee</p><p>Anger is 1150 hate per proc, using WA5 and no Combat Effects as baseline, that's 4 procs per minute since it's in primary for 4600 hate.</p><p>Total Hate on BBoB per minute, assuming max haste, WA5 and no combat effects is:</p><p>9385</p><p>If using 2.3 swings per minute as baseline, it would be 5002 in melee hate for a total of 9602 hate per minute.</p><p>Compare the Darkblade of the Warlord, which it turns out is actually a better hate generating weapon than BBoB...</p><p>53 Hate per swing (38+15)</p><p>Swing Rate 1.8</p><p>Hate per round at 2.2:  116.6</p><p>33.33 rounds per minute</p><p>3886.3 Melee Hate (2.2)</p><p>4062.9 melee hate (2.3)</p><p>Procs per minute with WA5, no combat effects:  5.2</p><p>HPM in procs: 5980</p><p>Total at 2.2:  9866.3</p><p>Total at 2.3: 10,042</p><p>The Darkblade of the Warlord actually generates more hate per minute than our 4 expansion old Brutish Blade.</p><p> </p><p> </p>
				
